{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·003.1", "text_original": "衡門之下，可以棲遲。泌之洋洋，可以樂飢。", "text_normalized": "衡門之下，可以棲遲。泌之洋洋，可以樂飢。", "notes": "衡門 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·003.2", "text_original": "豈其食魚，必河之魴。豈其取妻，必齊之姜。", "text_normalized": "豈其食魚，必河之魴。豈其取妻，必齊之姜。", "notes": "衡門 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·003.3", "text_original": "豈其食魚，必河之鯉。豈其取妻，必宋之子。", "text_normalized": "豈其食魚，必河之鯉。豈其取妻，必宋之子。", "notes": "衡門 Chinese stanza 3."}
